name: Reebok ASTROFOAM Sneakers BD2203 Navy
short_description:
Soft is the new fast. Discover comfort that propels you forward in our Reebok ASTROFOAM sneakers. 360-degree cushioning delivers a luxurious feel from the first step, while the seamless FuseFrame upper maximizes breathability and style.
FuseFrame and mesh upper for breathable support
Low-cut design for freedom of motion and quicker transitions
ASTROFOAM bottom technology for 360-degree cushioning
Delta logo on the side
Rubber hits on the toe and heel for traction

You don't let anything hold you back, not even your shoes. Take your training to the next level in these featherweight Yourflex trainers. This sneaker comes equipped with the lightest and most flexible sole in our training line, meaning you can tackle any workout without extra weigh-down.

Ultralight outsole for maximum flexibility

name: Reebok SUBLITE TRAIN 4.0 Sneakers AR3403 Alloy
short_description:
As you strive toward all-around fitness, our SubLite 4.0 stabilises your every plate-weighted step at the gym and each lateral-lunging bound out on the field. The ultralight, heel-lifting build absorbs each impact and propels you forward. The Pivot Point bottom tracks with your sharp-turn agility to add finesse to your moves.

Tricot and mesh upper with diamond-shaped overlays for lightweight breathable support
Low-cut design for ankle mobility and an Adaptalink+ microweb spider tongue for locked-in stability
Sublite C50d EVA foam midsole for high-tech, ultralight cushioning
8mm heel-to-toe drop for a traditional feel and ride
Minimal rubber on the outsole for maximum traction
Forefoot flex grooves and a base pivot point for flexibility and precision
Removable sockliner for accommodating orthotics
